OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain. Drier and brighter weather
OL,7,Fwill arrive from the west during the
OL,8,Fmorning then some good sunny spells in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Feeling rather cold in
OL,10,Fthe fresh southwesterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear spells with a few
OL,13,Fshowers moving through on the strong
OL,14,Fwesterly or southwesterly breeze. It
OL,15,Fwill be a rather cold night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA bright day with sunny
OL,18,Fspells and a few passing showers.
OL,19,FFeeling rather cold with a fresh or
OL,20,Fstrong westerly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
