OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and bright on Wednesday but
OL,7,Fsoutherly winds becoming strong. Rain
OL,8,Fbands moving east followed by drier
OL,9,Fand brighter spells for the rest of
OL,10,Fthe week.
